title: Week 2 preview & Jets vs. Bills recap
itunes:title: Week 2 preview & Jets vs. Bills recap
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling, and Marc Sessler –  go game-by-game breaking down each Week 2 matchup, and pick which teams they think are a “lock” this week. Plus, the heroes recap the Thursday night matchup in Buffalo between the Jets and the Bills.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
